      "translations": {
        "en": "――Magical Mirai 10th Anniversary",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "in VENUS STAGE",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in VENUS STAGE",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本イベントにトリエル出演が決まった数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A few days after TRINITYAiLE was\nselected to perform at this event",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、ミクの呼び出し方は……\nこれで良かったかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ if I want to call Miku…\nIs this how I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1993.1654612000002,
          "startTime": 14.6264987945
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは、{user}さん\nどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ {user}-san.\nWhat's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7606742859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ミク、いきなり呼び出してすまない\nトリエルのみんなが作詞に苦戦してるみたいなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku‚ sorry for calling you out of the blue.\nIt seems that everyone from TRINITYAiLE is struggling with the lyrics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.0606742859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "初めての試みだから無理もないが……\nそれで、ミクに相談出来ないかなと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's their first attempt‚ so it's understandable…\nSo‚ I thought maybe I can ask some advice from you‚ Miku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8606742859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！　私も作詞の経験はないけど……\n協力出来ることがあるなら頑張るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! I don't have experience with lyrics‚ but…\nI'll do my best if there's anything I can do to help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、何か言葉を掛けるなら……\n私はもっといろいろと知らないといけないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you want me to have a conversatoin with them…\nI need to know more about various things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku004.m4a",
      "text": "私はバーチャルの世界にいるから\nデータベースで公式情報を調べることが出来るけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I exist in the virtual world‚\nso I can look up official information in the database…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5940076192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku005.m4a",
      "text": "もっと深いこと――トリエルのみんなが\nどんな人なのかを私は知らないなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don't know deeper things—like what kind of people\neveryone from TRINITYAiLE is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、{user}さんにいろいろと\n教えてほしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I want you to tell me various things‚\n{user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}